; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">In December 2020, the newly formed Varda raised a $9=
 million Seed round co-led by Founders Fund and Lux Capital.&#160;</p><p st=
yle=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px=
 0;">Varda now had the money and the expertise to send things from the heav=
ens back down to earth, but they still needed to figure out how to make thi=
